# AutoX Test Automation

When writing or editing AutoX test XML in this project, follow these rules.

## Required reading

Before creating or modifying test suite XML, read:

1. `docs/autox-llm/README.md` — documentation index
2. `docs/autox-llm/reference/README.md` — API reference index by Group
3. The relevant how-to guide and API reference for your task type (see table below)

## Task → documentation lookup

| Task | How-to guide | API reference (steps) | API reference (validations) |
|------|--------------|----------------------|----------------------------|
| Control flow / loops / if | `11-language-steps.md` | `reference/steps-lang.md` | `reference/validations-lang.md` |
| SQL / database | `12-sql-automation.md` | `reference/steps-rdbms.md` | `reference/validations-rdbms.md` |
